OL,6,F"Lads jumped on my car, they damaged
OL,7,Fmy car, bonnet, screen, roof, windows,
OL,8,Feverything," Mr Akhtar explains.
OL,10,FAs they set fire to other vehicles
OL,11,Fnearby, he was forced to hide upstairs
OL,12,Fwith his young children.
OL,14,F"My 11 year-old son was holding my
OL,15,Fhand, he said to me 'dad, save me,
OL,16,Fsave me.' I said, 'don't worry, they
OL,17,Fwon't come in', but I'm scared myself.
OL,18,FWe thought maybe they'd come inside
OL,19,Fand kill us. We heard that they were
OL,20,Flooking for Asian people."
