OL,6,FSix weeks on from the riots, the
OL,7,FTonight programme has been analysing
OL,8,Fthe online activity that inspired the
OL,9,Foffline violence that terrified
OL,10,Ffamilies like Mr Akhtar's.
OL,12,FNew data shared with us shows the
OL,13,Fextraordinary rise in far-right
OL,14,Ftraffic on social media.
OL,16,FOn Telegram, activity surged in the 48
OL,17,Fhours after the Southport attack, in
OL,18,Fwhich three young girls were killed.
