OL,6,FWe spoke to one of Robinson's former
OL,7,Fcomrades, Ivan Humble, who has the
OL,8,Fletters EDL tattooed on his right arm,
OL,9,Fbut now works to counter the views he
OL,10,Fonce held.
OL,12,FAs a former regional organiser for the
OL,13,Ffar-right group, he told us online
OL,14,Fplatforms are radicalising minds at a
OL,15,Fterrifying rate.
OL,17,F"You're always seeing stories posted
OL,18,Fin there that nobody challenges,
OL,19,Fbecause the minute somebody challenges
OL,20,Fthe mindset of the group you're kicked
OL,21,Fout of the group and blocked.
