OL,6,FThousands of officers put their safety
OL,7,Fon the line during the unrest, but
OL,8,Fsome believe they wouldn't have had to
OL,9,Fif more action had been taken earlier
OL,10,Fto counter the threat of the far-right.
OL,12,FFor several years, there have been
OL,13,Fwarnings about the rise of far right
OL,14,Fextremism, which we encountered at ITV
OL,15,FNews in 2021 when we were allowed to
OL,16,Ffilm on the terrorist wings of two
OL,17,Fprisons.
OL,19,FAnd yet some believe the police have
OL,20,Fnot taken the threat seriously enough.
