OL,6,FFormer superintendent at the
OL,7,FMetropolitan Police, Leroy Logan, told
OL,8,Fme: "I think when it comes to these
OL,9,Friots, they haven't taken the far
OL,10,Fright seriously enough for a number of
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,F"So they haven't devoted the assets to
OL,14,Finfiltrate, to really understand the
OL,15,Fscale of it. I think they do now.
OL,16,FInfiltration is critical. But I don't
OL,17,Fthink the infiltration that they
OL,18,Fshould have had was there."
